\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Can you remember the first time you met her parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Her parents? Oh I've known them all my life practically. Oh yes. I've known of them you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 There wasn't the or deal of you being introduced to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh no, no, no. Oh I'd known of them, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Can you remember the first time you went into their home, was that before you decided to got married or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh was in the home well before the - decided to get married. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 What was her father's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh - her father. Now - her grandfather was Downey - John Downey. He built - \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 of Musselburgh. And my father built - the other half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 So the families would know each other that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Her father was in the building trade too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
No. Her father was Bernie MacFarlane, the great golfer to Willie Park. A professional golfer. Was it - is it Barnton, is there such as place as Barnton? A golf course? Aye, well Barnton or something, he was the professi
onal golfer there. And he - and he worked with many - he worked with Willie Park - and he died very young, only young, and then her mother came home - and took - looked after her father's business for the building you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Were you treated as one of the family or as a guest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh family. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 After you were married did you get on well with your parents-in-law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you go and visit them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you ever help them with odd jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 What did you call them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Just - granny. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Before you were married what would you call her parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh Mrs McFarlane. Aye.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 It was after your children were born you called her granny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Called granny, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Your wife would know your parents too then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
Yes. You see, we both lost the father's. Her father was dead you see. And my - father, he was dead too. So there were only my mother - and her mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was she the first girl you'd brought home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 And your mother and her mother knew each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Do you remember when you first started courting how often you would see each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh dear. Well - you - wee seen a lot of each other in the mornings, because s
he went to business and got the train in the morning. That was one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you go out together in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh yes, on a Saturday especially. Always went to some - football match, cricket match, tennis match or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 She went to what you wanted to go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
Yes, yes. And she - she was interested in tennis and - and golf and that. So we went to all these sort of things on - on the - on the Saturdays. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did just the two of you go or did you go with a group of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh 
no, just two of us. Oh sometimes we met - people when we got there you know. But we - we'd always - before that we had always - a group used to have - what - when you said a group we used to have the farmers from Kierney, White Craigs, and - that was a gr
oup, and used to form and said, oh look here, we'll have a party. We'll go}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15884563\charrsid11028862  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
to - Mrs Elders, we'll got to Kierney's, we'll go round, and - the girls would all make - different things and we went to these houses, and this is what they call the surprise party,
 we just walked in and took the - we used to have great fun that way. That - that was how we made our fun. And - this - this physical culture classes and that. We never had picture houses, theatres or - or anything. No, nothing - nothing like that at all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Can you remember a moment when you actually decided to get married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you say to her, will you marry me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh yes. I couldn't tell you. But I - I think my mother was one of the main ones that said, here it's time you're getting your skates on.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Your mother did it did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Aye. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have to ask her mother's permission?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh yes, had to ask her mother's permission, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was she with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, no. Went on my own, yes. Oh yes. But - well, it's - you know, you're going back a - a long - a long time now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you exchange rings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. No. No. I gave her an -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 You gave her a ring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you choose it or did you both choose it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, both choose it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have an announcement in the paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
Yes. Half a minute now. Had we announcement, I can't just tell you about that because there were very - you know what I mean, very shy, my wife and - you know what I mean? Didn't want any publicity or anything else.
 May not - I don't think we had an announcement.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have a party or presents or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
No. We - we had a party. Engagement party, that was all. But what I mean by party I don't mean up to Mulbray's Hotel, it was just - in the house, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 When you chose your wedding ring did your wife go with you or did you choose it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 She went - oh she went, she chose it. Aye, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Have you given any rings since you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No. No. No, doesn't want rings. She's got - two. Yes. Aye. A ring for her nose or her ears.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you ever exchange any other kind of tokens, in some part of the country they have love spoons for instance that you exchange?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No. No. No, nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 You said that you saved up and you found a house before you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you buy any household equipment before you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes, when we went along we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 And you said your mother helped you to set up home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes. We - we went and we had lots of 
- things we picked up - at sales you know. That is before we were married. And when we were married. Then mother - then her - my wife's mother she helped us too. She - she furnished a lot of the rooms - and that was in Inveresk Road where we went first.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 When you first decided about the wedding who was the first person you went to see to arrange about the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 To arrange. The first person we went to was the minister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Than the hotel afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Then - the Woodside Hotel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How long before the wedding did you go to see the minister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How long before the wedding? Oh - I don't remember now, just - we went some time before the wedding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was it weeks or months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh it would be months - months anyway - because - because - a
t that time for April - it's always busy, the old minister. I - I happened to be in his kirk hers and we were all - and my wife was a member of his kirk too. So he said, oh yes, right away I'll put that in my diary. Then we went and - we wondered where we
 would go for the reception or to get married, whether the church or to - to go away up to Inveresk, the big church away up there, we thought, well Woodside would be the best just down there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was there any particular reason for the date that you chose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
No. I - I - that's been a great argument with myself and my wife, a great argument. She chose the eighteenth of April, and damn it all if she had chosen the fourth of April I could have got an income tax rebate. It was - she said - eighteenth of Ap
ril. I said, oh. She - she just missed it, so she - it was her for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 You wouldn't have any difficulty getting your mother's agreement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh none whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you want a large or a small wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Small wedding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How did you decide who to invite?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 My wife - put down her friends - and I put down her friends and we compared them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How were people invited at that time, did they just ask them to come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No. No. Sent a card.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did anyone have to come and stay overnight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
No. No. Oh - well my - half one minute now. No, my - my - my brother was up from London, he - he stayed - he was staying with - Jimmy, with my mother you see. No, no. No, no. Nobody else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How were the costs of the wedding met? Did you have to pay for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, no. No. My - my wife's - you see, she paid for the - well - her mother paid for it all, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you do anything special the last week before the wedding, such as a stage party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did anything happen on your last day at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
No. No. No, you just knew - you know what I mean the boss knew. That was the only one. And - aye, at Morningside it was and - and I got a present from them and I just came away - oh no, there were no - none of this, and my wife left lo
ng before she - give her her notice she was going. She never said why. That's the reason it wasn't in the papers, our engagement. So -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you see the bride on the wedding day before the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes, I think so, I couldn't tell you whether I did or not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 You weren't superstitious about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
I don't think so. Well - if it's superstitious I wouldn't have seen her because the Fisherrow people are very superstitious. You know what I mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Do you remember what you both wore for the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Aye, tails and the old tall hat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have to hire them or did you buy them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, I had them. I - I was an elder in the church. I had them for that, and my wife was in white, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was it a long dress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes, a long dress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Do you know if she wore something old, something new, something borrowed, something blue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
Oh she wore - she - something like that because - I remember her running around saying - something - about - something old, something new and all this nons
ense so she was to wear something - I - I - I couldn't tell you but I think she did, she wore - something old something new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did she have any attendants, bridesmaids?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Ah, was there bridesmaids, yes. Ella Finaly, the girl who worked in Brentons, 
and there was Ethel and - Peggy, Peggy, oh I forget, Peggy Mackenzie, aye, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did your bride ever wear her wedding dress again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Who gave her away?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Her brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was there a best man and ushers and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes, the best man was my brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you wear flowers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 I had a flower, yes, and she had flowers, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Can you remember what happened to the flowers afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh - couldn't tell you. The usual thing when a wedding like that happens - you go to t
he churchyard and put on some of the graves. That - that may have - that possibly would have happened. I - I would think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Do you know they bride and groom's guests are separated in a church, there's the bride's side and the groom's side?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Why 
they are separate? Well - the groom's side and the bride's side, I - I know what you mean. I can't tell you - why this - why they're separated. You think they're going to fight or something? I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Were there any presents given to the bride at the wedding, such as a horseshoe or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
She got something from the old fishwives you know. She may have got - she - she got something - from the old - from - from some of the fishwives, because - she - she was in the back of Fisherrow
, the fishwives all standing there. Aye, she - she got some - something like a horseshoe or something, I - I forget what it was. I think it was a horseshoe, tied, you know, with ribbons on it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Were any photographs taken?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have confetti or rice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh - confetti and - and rice, every blessed thing. A lot of mess.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 You had your reception in the hotel where you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How were the guests received, did you line up and shake hands with everybody or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes. Yes. They shook hands with - my - mother and - and Mrs MacFarlane \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 see. The - they all came round and - shook hands, and they just - mixed with each other and sat down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was it a sitting down meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Sitting down meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Can you remember how the seating was arranged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 The top table I remember was - my wife, myself, the best}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15884563\charrsid11028862 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 man my brother, and my wife's brother, her mother and my mother. That's how the top table was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Were the other people on tables off the top table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 And the minister - the minister. The minister was at the top. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did they have separate little tables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, no, just one table, long table, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you have a wedding cake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did it have decorations on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Decorations, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Do you remember anything special you had on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No. No. No. The usual flowers and usual decorations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you eat the cake at the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes, the cake was cut at the wedding. And that bit round as - was - to each one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 What happened with what was left over?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh - that - that was - we got that when we came home. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you eat it or did you keep it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh we ate - we ate it, it - it was a lot of frinkets in it you know, horseshoes and three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15884563\charrsid11028862  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 penny pieces and all that sort of thing. In the mixture, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Were there any speeches?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Who made speeches, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 The minister - spoke for a heck of a long time, I
 was glad of it too. Myself and Jimmy Bruce the fishmonger, the - the fish curer, Newhaven. And my brother. And - my - wife's brother. Like that, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Was there any dancing and singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 No, no. It was afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 After the meal was that the end of the reception?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 The end, yes, they went off at about five or six o'clock you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 You went on honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 When did you leave the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 We left the wedding at - oh let me see - just about four or five o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 So the wedding just sort of continued to about an hour afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Were there any practical jokes played on you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Yes. But - we - had the car all tied up and everything else, but - it was a false car bec
ause - we didn't go in that car, we had our car round the corner. Tommy Hudson took us round the corner, he drove us right to the station.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 How long were you away for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh - fortnight, three weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did you carry the bride over the threshold when you got home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 The what? Oh carry her over the - no I did not. No. We were glad to get home because we were roasted alive down in Llandudno.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Do you remember attending any other weddings when you were young which were totally different from your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh yes, some of the Fisherrow weddings, oh my God.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 What happened at them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Oh they - they - the right hullabaloo at these things you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Would it be a church wedding or a hall wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 A hall wedding, you know, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15884563\charrsid11028862 they're all - Jock Thomson's ba}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
rns are all there and they're all shouting - their heads off. That was one, another one was a farm wedding. Bully Bean, Nancy - Maxwell, that was - that was a pretty rough wedding too. Oh yes dancing and all - yes. And, oh yes, 
Alistair MacKensie's, that was a - long wedding too. That - that was the usual thing with the Fisher people, to have a meal you see, and a dance after it. And the dance would go right on 'til next morning. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3934310 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 Did they invite a lot of people to the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8078847 GA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16216466\charrsid11028862 
Oh yes, all the Fisher people, but - we - we - that's the reason I - I thought well, it's far better cutting all this out, and just having your own - just having your own people. Didn't want a show or a fuss. Having all the fishwives all down
. Oh no, no. So that's - that's what we done. And that's what we did.
\par }}